==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncrown
<hw>Un*crown"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>crown</ets>.]</ety> <def>To deprive of a crown; to
take the crown from; hence, to discrown; to dethrone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He hath done me wrong,⟦br⟧
And therefore I'll <qex>uncrown</qex> him ere't be long.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncrudded</ent>⟦br⟧
